  user_input {
    user_response: "Apply the \"Immersive UI\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Immersive UI\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"bg-zinc-950 text-zinc-300 font-sans h-[768px] w-[1024px] flex flex-col overflow-hidden border-4 border-zinc-900 select-none\\\">\\n  <!-- TOP NAVIGATION / SYSTEM STATUS -->\\n  <header class=\\\"h-14 border-b border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950 flex items-center justify-between px-6 shrink-0\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-4\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-600 animate-pulse\\\"></div>\\n      <h1 class=\\\"font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-zinc-100 font-bold\\\">Culling Game // Central Control Panel</h1>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"flex gap-8 font-mono text-[10px] text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex flex-col items-end\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-zinc-400\\\">System Clock</span>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-emerald-400\\\">23:59:58 UTC-09</span>\\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"flex flex-col items-end border-l border-zinc-800 pl-8\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-zinc-400\\\">Encryption</span>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-purple-400\\\">Grade 1 Static</span>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </header>\\n\\n  <div class=\\\"flex flex-1 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n    <!-- LEFT PANEL: REGISTRATION ZONE -->\\n    <aside class=\\\"w-[320px] bg-zinc-900/50 border-r border-zinc-800 p-6 flex flex-col shrink-0\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"mb-8\\\">\\n        <h2 class=\\\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-zinc-500 mb-6 flex items-center gap-2\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"w-4 h-[1px] bg-zinc-700\\\"></span> Player Registration\\n        </h2>\\n        \\n        <div class=\\\"space-y-5\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n            <label class=\\\"text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider text-zinc-500 font-bold\\\">Sorcerer Name</label>\\n            <input type=\\\"text\\\" placeholder=\\\"e.g. Megumi Fushiguro\\\" class=\\\"w-full bg-zinc-950 border border-zinc-800 rounded px-3 py-2 text-sm text-zinc-100 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-purple-500 focus:border-purple-500 placeholder:text-zinc-700\\\">\\n          </div>\\n          \\n          <div class=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n            <label class=\\\"text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider text-zinc-500 font-bold\\\">Starting Colony</label>\\n            <select class=\\\"w-full bg-zinc-950 border border-zinc-800 rounded px-3 py-2 text-sm text-zinc-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-purple-500\\\">\\n              <option>Tokyo Colony 1</option>\\n              <option>Tokyo Colony 2</option>\\n              <option>Sendai Colony</option>\\n              <option>Sakurajima Colony</option>\\n            </select>\\n          </div>\\n          \\n          <div class=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n            <label class=\\\"text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider text-zinc-500 font-bold\\\">Cursed Technique Specification</label>\\n            <textarea rows=\\\"4\\\" placeholder=\\\"Describe innate technique...\\\" class=\\\"w-full bg-zinc-950 border border-zinc-800 rounded px-3 py-2 text-sm text-zinc-100 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-purple-500 focus:border-purple-500 placeholder:text-zinc-700 resize-none\\\"></textarea>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"mt-auto\\\">\\n        <button class=\\\"w-full bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700 text-white font-bold py-4 rounded text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(220,38,38,0.2)] flex items-center justify-center gap-2 transition-all\\\">\\n          <span>Enter the Culling Game</span>\\n        </button>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-[8px] text-zinc-600 text-center mt-3 uppercase tracking-tighter\\\">Warning: Binding vow active upon submission.</p>\\n      </div>\\n    </aside>\\n\\n    <!-- RIGHT PANEL: MONITORING GRID -->\\n    <main class=\\\"flex-1 flex flex-col bg-zinc-950 relative\\\">\\n      <!-- SCANLINE OVERLAY EFFECT -->\\n      <div class=\\\"absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-[0.03] bg-[linear-gradient(rgba(18,16,16,0)_50%,rgba(0,0,0,0.25)_50%),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,0,0,0.06),rgba(0,255,0,0.02),rgba(0,0,255,0.06))] bg-[length:100%_2px,3px_100%]\\\"></div>\\n\\n      <!-- MONITORING HEADER -->\\n      <div class=\\\"h-20 flex items-center px-8 border-b border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950/80 backdrop-blur-sm shrink-0\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-12\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"flex flex-col\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase text-zinc-500 tracking-widest\\\">Active Sorcerers</span>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-3xl font-mono text-zinc-100\\\">1,402</span>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex flex-col border-l border-zinc-800 pl-12\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase text-zinc-500 tracking-widest\\\">Total Points Distributed</span>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-3xl font-mono text-purple-400\\\">42,850</span>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- CARDS GRID -->\\n      <div class=\\\"flex-1 p-8 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 h-full\\\">\\n          <!-- PLAYER CARD 1 -->\\n          <div class=\\\"bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 p-5 rounded-lg flex flex-col shadow-lg border-l-4 border-l-emerald-500\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start mb-4\\\">\\n              <h3 class=\\\"text-zinc-100 font-bold text-base\\\">Yuji Itadori</h3>\\n              <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-1.5\\\">\\n                <span class=\\\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-400\\\"></span>\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[9px] uppercase tracking-tighter text-emerald-400\\\">Alive</span>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[9px] uppercase text-zinc-500 tracking-widest mb-1\\\">Colony 1 // Tokyo</span>\\n            <div class=\\\"text-4xl font-mono text-purple-400 font-black mt-2\\\">20</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"mt-auto pt-4 flex gap-2\\\">\\n              <button class=\\\"flex-1 bg-zinc-950 border border-zinc-800 py-2 rounded text-[10px] font-mono hover:bg-zinc-800 text-zinc-400\\\">-1 POINT</button>\\n              <button class=\\\"flex-1 bg-zinc-950 border border-zinc-800 py-2 rounded text-[10px] font-mono hover:bg-zinc-800 text-purple-400\\\">+1 POINT</button>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <!-- PLAYER CARD 2 -->\\n          <div class=\\\"bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 p-5 rounded-lg flex flex-col shadow-lg border-l-4 border-l-red-500\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start mb-4\\\">\\n              <h3 class=\\\"text-zinc-500 font-bold text-base line-through\\\">Hajime Kashimo</h3>\\n              <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-1.5\\\">\\n                <span class=\\\"text-red-500 text-xs\\\">\303\227</span>\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[9px] uppercase tracking-tighter text-red-500\\\">Deceased</span>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[9px] uppercase text-zinc-500 tracking-widest mb-1\\\">Sendai Colony</span>\\n            <div class=\\\"text-4xl font-mono text-zinc-700 font-black mt-2\\\">159</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"mt-auto pt-4 flex gap-2\\\">\\n              <button class=\\\"flex-1 bg-zinc-950/50 border border-zinc-800/50 py-2 rounded text-[10px] font-mono cursor-not-allowed text-zinc-700\\\">LOCKED</button>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <!-- PLAYER CARD 3 -->\\n          <div class=\\\"bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 p-5 rounded-lg flex flex-col shadow-lg border-l-4 border-l-emerald-500\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start mb-4\\\">\\n              <h3 class=\\\"text-zinc-100 font-bold text-base\\\">Yuta Okkotsu</h3>\\n              <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-1.5\\\">\\n                <span class=\\\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-400\\\"></span>\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[9px] uppercase tracking-tighter text-emerald-400\\\">Alive</span>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[9px] uppercase text-zinc-500 tracking-widest mb-1\\\">Sendai Colony</span>\\n            <div class=\\\"text-4xl font-mono text-purple-400 font-black mt-2\\\">190</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"mt-auto pt-4 flex gap-2\\\">\\n              <button class=\\\"flex-1 bg-zinc-950 border border-zinc-800 py-2 rounded text-[10px] font-mono hover:bg-zinc-800 text-zinc-400\\\">-1 POINT</button>\\n              <button class=\\\"flex-1 bg-zinc-950 border border-zinc-800 py-2 rounded text-[10px] font-mono hover:bg-zinc-800 text-purple-400\\\">+1 POINT</button>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <!-- PLAYER CARD 4 -->\\n          <div class=\\\"bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 p-5 rounded-lg flex flex-col shadow-lg border-l-4 border-l-emerald-500\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start mb-4\\\">\\n              <h3 class=\\\"text-zinc-100 font-bold text-base\\\">Maki Zenin</h3>\\n              <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-1.5\\\">\\n                <span class=\\\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-400\\\"></span>\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[9px] uppercase tracking-tighter text-emerald-400\\\">Alive</span>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[9px] uppercase text-zinc-500 tracking-widest mb-1\\\">Sakurajima Colony</span>\\n            <div class=\\\"text-4xl font-mono text-purple-400 font-black mt-2\\\">0</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"mt-auto pt-4 flex gap-2\\\">\\n              <button class=\\\"flex-1 bg-zinc-950 border border-zinc-800 py-2 rounded text-[10px] font-mono hover:bg-zinc-800 text-zinc-400\\\">-1 POINT</button>\\n              <button class=\\\"flex-1 bg-zinc-950 border border-zinc-800 py-2 rounded text-[10px] font-mono hover:bg-zinc-800 text-purple-400\\\">+1 POINT</button>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <!-- PLAYER CARD 5 -->\\n          <div class=\\\"bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 p-5 rounded-lg flex flex-col shadow-lg border-l-4 border-l-emerald-500\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start mb-4\\\">\\n              <h3 class=\\\"text-zinc-100 font-bold text-base\\\">Hiromi Higuruma</h3>\\n              <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-1.5\\\">\\n                <span class=\\\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-400\\\"></span>\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[9px] uppercase tracking-tighter text-emerald-400\\\">Alive</span>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[9px] uppercase text-zinc-500 tracking-widest mb-1\\\">Colony 1 // Tokyo</span>\\n            <div class=\\\"text-4xl font-mono text-purple-400 font-black mt-2\\\">102</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"mt-auto pt-4 flex gap-2\\\">\\n              <button class=\\\"flex-1 bg-zinc-950 border border-zinc-800 py-2 rounded text-[10px] font-mono hover:bg-zinc-800 text-zinc-400\\\">-1 POINT</button>\\n              <button class=\\\"flex-1 bg-zinc-950 border border-zinc-800 py-2 rounded text-[10px] font-mono hover:bg-zinc-800 text-purple-400\\\">+1 POINT</button>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <!-- PLAYER CARD 6 -->\\n          <div class=\\\"bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 p-5 rounded-lg flex flex-col shadow-lg border-l-4 border-l-emerald-500\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start mb-4\\\">\\n              <h3 class=\\\"text-zinc-100 font-bold text-base\\\">Kinji Hakari</h3>\\n              <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-1.5\\\">\\n                <span class=\\\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-400 animate-pulse\\\"></span>\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[9px] uppercase tracking-tighter text-emerald-400\\\">Jackpot Active</span>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[9px] uppercase text-zinc-500 tracking-widest mb-1\\\">Colony 2 // Tokyo</span>\\n            <div class=\\\"text-4xl font-mono text-purple-400 font-black mt-2\\\">5</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"mt-auto pt-4 flex gap-2\\\">\\n              <button class=\\\"flex-1 bg-zinc-950 border border-zinc-800 py-2 rounded text-[10px] font-mono hover:bg-zinc-800 text-zinc-400\\\">-1 POINT</button>\\n              <button class=\\\"flex-1 bg-zinc-950 border border-zinc-800 py-2 rounded text-[10px] font-mono hover:bg-zinc-800 text-purple-400\\\">+1 POINT</button>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </main>\\n  </div>\\n\\n  <!-- FOOTER STATUS BAR -->\\n  <footer class=\\\"h-8 bg-zinc-900 border-t border-zinc-800 flex items-center px-6 shrink-0 gap-8\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2\\\">\\n      <span class=\\\"w-2 h-2 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full\\\"></span>\\n      <span class=\\\"text-[8px] font-mono text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-tighter\\\">Network: Stable (Vow-Bound)</span>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2\\\">\\n      <span class=\\\"text-[8px] font-mono text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-tighter\\\">Data Stream: ID-88219-JK</span>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"ml-auto text-[8px] font-mono text-zinc-600 uppercase tracking-tighter italic\\\">\\n      \\\"The Game persists as long as rules are obeyed.\\\"\\n    </div>\\n  </footer>\\n</div>\\n                    </body>\\n                  </html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
    items {
      text: "Apply the \"Immersive UI\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Immersive UI\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"bg-zinc-950 text-zinc-300 font-sans h-[768px] w-[1024px] flex flex-col overflow-hidden border-4 border-zinc-900 select-none\\\">\\n  <!-- TOP NAVIGATION / SYSTEM STATUS -->\\n  <header class=\\\"h-14 border-b border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950 flex items-center justify-between px-6 shrink-0\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-4\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-600 animate-pulse\\\"></div>\\n      <h1 class=\\\"font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-zinc-100 font-bold\\\">Culling Game // Central Control Panel</h1>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"flex gap-8 font-mono text-[10px] text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex flex-col items-end\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-zinc-400\\\">System Clock</span>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-emerald-400\\\">23:59:58 UTC-09</span>\\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"flex flex-col items-end border-l border-zinc-800 pl-8\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-zinc-400\\\">Encryption</span>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-purple-400\\\">Grade 1 Static</span>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </header>\\n\\n  <div class=\\\"flex flex-1 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n    <!-- LEFT PANEL: REGISTRATION ZONE -->\\n    <aside class=\\\"w-[320px] bg-zinc-900/50 border-r border-zinc-800 p-6 flex flex-col shrink-0\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"mb-8\\\">\\n        <h2 class=\\\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-zinc-500 mb-6 flex items-center gap-2\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"w-4 h-[1px] bg-zinc-700\\\"></span> Player Registration\\n        </h2>\\n        \\n        <div class=\\\"space-y-5\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n            <label class=\\\"text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider text-zinc-500 font-bold\\\">Sorcerer Name</label>\\n            <input type=\\\"text\\\" placeholder=\\\"e.g. Megumi Fushiguro\\\" class=\\\"w-full bg-zinc-950 border border-zinc-800 rounded px-3 py-2 text-sm text-zinc-100 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-purple-500 focus:border-purple-500 placeholder:text-zinc-700\\\">\\n          </div>\\n          \\n          <div class=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n            <label class=\\\"text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider text-zinc-500 font-bold\\\">Starting Colony</label>\\n            <select class=\\\"w-full bg-zinc-950 border border-zinc-800 rounded px-3 py-2 text-sm text-zinc-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-purple-500\\\">\\n              <option>Tokyo Colony 1</option>\\n              <option>Tokyo Colony 2</option>\\n              <option>Sendai Colony</option>\\n              <option>Sakurajima Colony</option>\\n            </select>\\n          </div>\\n          \\n          <div class=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n            <label class=\\\"text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider text-zinc-500 font-bold\\\">Cursed Technique Specification</label>\\n            <textarea rows=\\\"4\\\" placeholder=\\\"Describe innate technique...\\\" class=\\\"w-full bg-zinc-950 border border-zinc-800 rounded px-3 py-2 text-sm text-zinc-100 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-purple-500 focus:border-purple-500 placeholder:text-zinc-700 resize-none\\\"></textarea>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"mt-auto\\\">\\n        <button class=\\\"w-full bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700 text-white font-bold py-4 rounded text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(220,38,38,0.2)] flex items-center justify-center gap-2 transition-all\\\">\\n          <span>Enter the Culling Game</span>\\n        </button>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-[8px] text-zinc-600 text-center mt-3 uppercase tracking-tighter\\\">Warning: Binding vow active upon submission.</p>\\n      </div>\\n    </aside>\\n\\n    <!-- RIGHT PANEL: MONITORING GRID -->\\n    <main class=\\\"flex-1 flex flex-col bg-zinc-950 relative\\\">\\n      <!-- SCANLINE OVERLAY EFFECT -->\\n      <div class=\\\"absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-[0.03] bg-[linear-gradient(rgba(18,16,16,0)_50%,rgba(0,0,0,0.25)_50%),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,0,0,0.06),rgba(0,255,0,0.02),rgba(0,0,255,0.06))] bg-[length:100%_2px,3px_100%]\\\"></div>\\n\\n      <!-- MONITORING HEADER -->\\n      <div class=\\\"h-20 flex items-center px-8 border-b border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950/80 backdrop-blur-sm shrink-0\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-12\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"flex flex-col\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase text-zinc-500 tracking-widest\\\">Active Sorcerers</span>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-3xl font-mono text-zinc-100\\\">1,402</span>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex flex-col border-l border-zinc-800 pl-12\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase text-zinc-500 tracking-widest\\\">Total Points Distributed</span>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-3xl font-mono text-purple-400\\\">42,850</span>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- CARDS GRID -->\\n      <div class=\\\"flex-1 p-8 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 h-full\\\">\\n          <!-- PLAYER CARD 1 -->\\n          <div class=\\\"bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 p-5 rounded-lg flex flex-col shadow-lg border-l-4 border-l-emerald-500\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start mb-4\\\">\\n              <h3 class=\\\"text-zinc-100 font-bold text-base\\\">Yuji Itadori</h3>\\n              <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-1.5\\\">\\n                <span class=\\\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-400\\\"></span>\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[9px] uppercase tracking-tighter text-emerald-400\\\">Alive</span>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[9px] uppercase text-zinc-500 tracking-widest mb-1\\\">Colony 1 // Tokyo</span>\\n            <div class=\\\"text-4xl font-mono text-purple-400 font-black mt-2\\\">20</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"mt-auto pt-4 flex gap-2\\\">\\n              <button class=\\\"flex-1 bg-zinc-950 border border-zinc-800 py-2 rounded text-[10px] font-mono hover:bg-zinc-800 text-zinc-400\\\">-1 POINT</button>\\n              <button class=\\\"flex-1 bg-