          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_UNCHANGED
        }
        lines {
          text: "        <!-- Content -->"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_UNCHANGED
        }
        lines {
          text: "        <div class=\"p-6 overflow-y-auto scrollbar-thin space-y-4 text-xs font-mono leading-relaxed text-zinc-400\">"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_UNCHANGED
        }
        lines {
          text: "          <p class=\"text-zinc-300 italic mb-3\">\"Players are given points by killing other sorcerers. Points correspond to the life of J\305\253jutsu Sorcerers or Non-Sorcerers...\"</p>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_UNCHANGED
        }
        lines {
          text: "          "
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_UNCHANGED
        }
        lines {
          text: "          <div class=\"space-y-3.5\">"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_UNCHANGED
        }
        lines {
          text: "            <div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_UNCHANGED
        }
        lines {
          text: "              <span class=\"text-purple-400 font-bold block mb-1\">RULE 1 \342\200\242 DECLARATIVE PARTICIPATION</span>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_UNCHANGED
        }
        lines {
          text: "              <p>Upon gaining a cursed technique or waking up inside a barrier, players must declare participation in the Culling Game in their starting colony within 19 days.</p>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_UNCHANGED
        }
        lines {
          text: "            </div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_UNCHANGED
        }
        lines {
          text: "            <div class=\"h-px bg-zinc-800/80\"></div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_UNCHANGED
        }
        lines {
          text: "            <div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_UNCHANGED
        }
        lines {
          text: "              <span class=\"text-purple-400 font-bold block mb-1\">RULE 2 \342\200\242 PENALTY OF DEATH</span>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_UNCHANGED
        }
        lines {
          text: "              <p>Any player who breaks Rule 1 shall suffer cursed technique extraction, which inevitably results in immediate brain death and cardiac arrest.</p>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_UNCHANGED
        }
        lines {
          text: "            </div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_UNCHANGED
        }
        lines {
          text: "            <div class=\"h-px bg-zinc-800/80\"></div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_UNCHANGED
        }
        lines {
          text: "            <div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_UNCHANGED
        }
        lines {
          text: "              <span class=\"text-purple-400 font-bold block mb-1\">RULE 5 \342\200\242 ACQUIRING POINTS</span>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_UNCHANGED
        }
        lines {
          text: "              <p>Players obtain points by taking the life of other participants. Shaman/Sorcerer deaths yield 5 points. Non-shaman deaths yield 1 point.</p>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_UNCHANGED
        }
        lines {
          text: "            </div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_UNCHANGED
        }
        lines {
          text: "            <div class=\"h-px bg-zinc-800/80\"></div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_UNCHANGED
        }
        lines {
          text: "            <div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_UNCHANGED
        }
        lines {
          text: "              <span class=\"text-purple-400 font-bold block mb-1\">RULE 10 \342\200\242 POINT TRANSFER</span>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_UNCHANGED
        }
        lines {
          text: "              <p>Players may transfer any number of their points to another participant. Koganes will act as the intermediary agent for all score adjustments.</p>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_UNCHANGED
        }
        lines {
          text: "            </div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_UNCHANGED
        }
        lines {
          text: "            <div class=\"h-px bg-zinc-800/80\"></div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_UNCHANGED
        }
        lines {
          text: "            <div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_UNCHANGED
        }
        lines {
          text: "              <span class=\"text-purple-400 font-bold block mb-1\">RULE 11 \342\200\242 CUSTOM RULE ADDITION</span>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_UNCHANGED
        }
        lines {
          text: "              <p>Except where it would have a significant negative impact on the longevity of the game, players may spend 100 points to negotiate and add a new rule to the Game Board with their Kogane.</p>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_UNCHANGED
        }
        lines {
          text: "            </div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_UNCHANGED
        }
        lines {
          text: "          </div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_UNCHANGED
        }
        lines {
          text: "        </div>"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_UNCHANGED
        }
        lines {
          text: "        <!-- Footer -->"
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_UNCHANGED
        }
